Template: llm-systems-manager/admin-user
Type: string
Default: llmadmin
Description: Dashboard admin username:
 Username for the manager dashboard's admin login.

Template: llm-systems-manager/admin-password
Type: password
Description: Dashboard admin password:
 Leave blank to keep the built-in default (llmadmin / llmadmin) and change
 it later under Admin -> Authentication. Custom passwords need at least
 8 printable characters.

Template: llm-systems-manager/smtp-server
Type: string
Description: SMTP server for email alerts:
 Leave blank to configure later in
 /opt/llm-systems-manager/config/llm-systems.toml.

Template: llm-systems-manager/smtp-user
Type: string
Description: SMTP username:
 Account used to send alert emails (e.g. you@example.com).

Template: llm-systems-manager/smtp-password
Type: password
Description: SMTP app-password:
 Leave blank to disable email alerts.
